Nokia 9000 Communicator: the first smartphone to be built
E-mail and Internet in time-lapse: 20 years ago, the Nokia Communicator was launched.
The successors are now the world's rulers - its manufacturer was a disaster.
The device weighed almost a pound and was more than four times as heavy as an iPhone 5.
It was thicker and bigger, so it didn't fit well in the hand.
